org.wso2.carbon.identity.oauth.tokenprocessor

Interface TokenPersistenceProcessor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EncryptionDecryptionPersistenceProcessor, HashingPersistenceProcessor, PlainTextPersistenceProcessor

    public interface TokenPersistenceProcessor
    TokenPersistenceProcessor implementations are used to process keys and secrets just before storing them in the database. E.g. to encrypt tokens before storing them in the database. Implementations of this interface can be configured through the identity.xml.
